Text: i noticed this only had one tracker listed, http://tracker.openbittorrent.com/announcennShouldn\'t it have at least 2?  Considering Openbittorrent has been quite upsy-downsy lately :)nnI know there\'s the whole speculations where more peers = bigger swarm != better transfer.nnBrings up a point though, this could be seen as some good load testing for both the \"client\" side (utorrent, azureus, etc....) as well as the \"tracker\" end - which in this case, OpenBT gets to be the labrat :)
